rComments: Professor is very nice and easy going, seems like he wants to help students. His teaching style however doesn't align with the exams, all theory/information and on the exam he expects you to memorize, understand, synthesize and apply it to a given situation. The assignments were 0 help as they were step-by-step instructions which meant no thinking.
Laughs at you when you ask him questions!!

He is the nicest teacher that you can ever meet! He is very helpful, down to earth and friendly, and he answers all your questions patiently. He will even help you with all kinds of computer problems that you might have. The course is ok, but the labs are really time consuming!
sooo adorable. poor guy would do so much better with better public speaking skillzz. But he will do his best to help you even if it means going out of his way. great course
